# Transform Multi-Agent Analyzer → Autonomous Code Assistant

## Overview

Transform the existing **code analysis** system (text-in → text-out) into an **autonomous code assistant** that reads/writes real project files, creates new projects from scratch, and executes code — all driven by natural language prompts.

### Current Architecture (What We Have)

```
src/
├── config.py              ← HuggingFace config, env loader
├── llm/
│   ├── provider.py        ← LLMProvider protocol (duck-typing interface)
│   ├── client.py          ← Raw HTTP calls to HF API
│   └── huggingface.py     ← HuggingFaceLLM with retry
├── agents/
│   ├── base.py            ← BaseAgent ABC + AgentRegistry + AgentResult
│   ├── completion.py      ← Code completion (text → text)
│   ├── debug.py           ← Bug detection (text → text)
│   ├── explain.py         ← Code explanation (text → text)
│   └── test.py            ← Test generation (text → text)
├── tools/
│   ├── ast_parser.py      ← AST extraction (pure functions on strings)
│   ├── bug_detector.py    ← Static bug detection (pure functions)
│   └── context_extractor.py ← Cursor context (pure functions)
├── memory/
│   ├── store.py           ← MemoryStore (code snapshots, responses)
│   └── context.py         ← Read-only MemoryContext for agents
├── engine/
│   └── trigger.py         ← Event detection & agent routing
├── orchestration/
│   ├── tasks.py           ← TaskType, TaskDefinition, TaskRegistry
│   └── crew.py            ← CrewWorkflow orchestrator
└── ui/
    └── streamlit_app.py   ← Streamlit UI (paste code → analyze)
```

### Target Architecture (What We're Building)

```
SAME AS ABOVE, PLUS:
├── workspace/             ← [NEW] Runtime project files directory
├── src/
│   ├── file_manager.py    ← [NEW] PHASE 1 — File CRUD operations
│   ├── project_handler.py ← [NEW] PHASE 2 — Upload/init projects
│   ├── agents/
│   │   └── editor.py      ← [NEW] PHASE 3 — File-editing agent
│   │   └── creator.py     ← [NEW] PHASE 4 — Project creation agent
│   ├── file_selector.py   ← [NEW] PHASE 5 — Intelligent file targeting
│   ├── runner.py          ← [NEW] PHASE 6 — Code execution engine
│   ├── pipeline.py        ← [NEW] PHASE 7 — End-to-end pipeline
│   └── ui/
│       └── streamlit_app.py ← [MODIFY] PHASE 8 — Full assistant UI
```

