## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Workspace Location**: The plan uses `workspace/` directory inside the project root (`c:\Users\CSE\Documents\miltiagent234\workspace\`). Should we use a different location, like a temp directory or user-configurable path?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Execution Safety**: Phase 6 adds `subprocess` execution. Currently scoped to **Python files only** with a 30-second timeout. Do you want additional sandboxing (e.g., restricted imports, virtual environment isolation)?

> [!WARNING]
> **LLM Model Capability**: The current model (`Qwen/Qwen2.5-Coder-32B-Instruct`) is used for analysis. For file editing (Phase 3) and project creation (Phase 4), it needs to return **complete, valid code files**. The prompts are designed for this, but results depend on model quality. We can add validation/retry logic.

