## Dependency Graph (No Circular Dependencies)

```mermaid
graph TD
    config[config.py] --> file_manager[file_manager.py]
    config --> llm[llm/huggingface.py]
    
    file_manager --> project_handler[project_handler.py]
    file_manager --> runner[runner.py]
    file_manager --> file_selector[file_selector.py]
    
    llm --> editor[agents/editor.py]
    llm --> creator[agents/creator.py]
    llm --> file_selector
    
    file_manager --> editor
    file_manager --> creator
    
    editor --> pipeline[pipeline.py]
    creator --> pipeline
    file_selector --> pipeline
    runner --> pipeline
    project_handler --> pipeline
    
    pipeline --> ui[ui/streamlit_app.py]
    
    style config fill:#e1f5fe
    style file_manager fill:#c8e6c9
    style pipeline fill:#fff3e0
    style ui fill:#fce4ec
```

All arrows point **downward** — no circular dependencies. UI depends on pipeline, pipeline depends on components, components depend on config/llm.
